						<summary>

						<p>On another pillar in the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the central shrine in Vēdāraṇyēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Parāntaka I. Year 30: 936-37 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This records the gift of 100 <hi rend="italic">Īḻakkāśu</hi> by <hi rend="italic">Vīraśōḻa-Aṇukkaṉ</hi> Kāḍaṉ Mēlvāyil forburning a night lamp (<hi rend="italic">irā-viḷakku</hi>) in the hall<note n="192-1">See No. 492 below.</note>(<hi rend="italic">ambalam</hi>) built by Kaḍamba Bhaṭṭarof Tirumaṟaikkāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
